    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and a small chip on the hood, while the interior remains in great shape with minimal wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable choice for any buyer looking for a solid, dependable car.",
