    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a major project. The engine runs roughly and the transmission is showing signs of imminent failure, often slipping under load. Cosmetically, there is extensive rust on the undercarriage and body panels, and the interior shows heavy wear and tear. It is being sold strictly as-is for parts or a full restoration.",
